data.description: WOW What a home! Newer home featuring an attached garage, along with a large 2 car detached garage, plus over 5 acres! This home is close to everything you need but tucked away for all your privacy oasis needs as well! Portion of the large deck is also screened in so you can enjoy the fresh air any time of the day! Inside the rooms are spacious as well featuring a walk-in closet in the main bedroom, laundry on the first floor, and an open kitchen! Come visit your home today!
